::Terrataur/Pyrotaur/Aquataur::
       She nods and opens a com to Pyrotaur and Aquataur.  "Come to the 
conference room...  You don't know where that is do you...  Just track my com 
signal and meet me there."

       Pyrotaur and Aquataur get up from wherever they are and go toward the 
conference room.
